@base = http://127.0.0.1:8000

### Health check
GET {{base}}/health

### Create enquiry
POST {{base}}/enquiry
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "channel": "whatsapp",
  "customer_name": "Ava Patel",
  "message": "Whats the price for 6 players this Saturday at Breakout Escape Room?"
}

### Schedule follow-up
POST {{base}}/enquiry/{{enquiry_id}}/followup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "delay_minutes": 30,
  "template": "Checking in about your Breakout Escape Room booking."
}

### Escalate enquiry
POST {{base}}/enquiry/{{enquiry_id}}/escalate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Customer requested a refund for a cancelled booking."
}

### Get enquiry history
GET {{base}}/enquiry/{{enquiry_id}}/history
